text: Elizabeth Woolsey (December 28, 1908 - January 11, 1977) was an American alpine skier. She competed in the women's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:1977 deaths Category:American female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the United States Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Albuquerque, New Mexico
